title: Tough Guys (1986)
description:
Two elderly gangsters are released from prison only to find they have trouble fitting in as old men who still take no guff from anyone. Harry and Archie are released from prison ready to collect their Social Security. How could they get into trouble at their age? Let's count the ways; A parole officer who is a famous criminal groupie, Dead end where people don't know they are dealing with dangerous, though older, criminals, a hit man who can barely see, but who still has an outstanding contract on them. Does anyone still rob trains? Rated PG
